Microservices + DDD
https://habr.com/ru/post/493426/
1. Primary Adapters - services
2. SecondaryAdapters - repos, EmailSender, Logger, DistributedCache
3. Logic
  3.1. Entities - our domain objects ( Items, Users ect.)
  3.2 DomainServices - actions or calculations over entities.
  
 Domain - domain area of our project
 
 BoundedContext - isolated part of application with some particular responsobility. Example: Bucket in ECommerce.
 
